snippet.title: NOOL PAROTTA | Thread Parotta Recipe Cooking In Village | Lachha Paratha | Soft Layered Parotta
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook a special thread parotta recipe. This parotta has different names in different places. In Karachi, it is called "Lachha Paratha." In our place, we call it "Nool Parotta." This Parotta has different layers: on the top, it's crunchy, and in the middle, it's very soft.

Parotta lovers can try it at home. The taste is very delicious!

snippet.title: Koolyug - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Welcome to Koolyug – jahan hoti hai virtual duniya aur asli emotions ki takraar! Amit, jo asli rishton ki ehmiyat samajhta hai, aur uski girlfriend Tanya, jise sirf fame aur followers ki fikr hai; ye dono khade hain ek ajeeb mod par. Likes aur comments ki race mein kya unka pyaar bacha rahega? Ya phir ek unexpected twist inki duniya ko hamesha ke liye badal dega? To dekho aur jano, Koolyug mein jo dikhai deta hai vo utna simple hota nahi.

snippet.title: Citadel: Honey Bunny - Official Trailer | Raj&DK | Russo Brothers | Varun, Samantha, Kay Kay, Saqib
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Citadel Honey Bunny Official Trailer 

About:
When stuntman Bunny recruits struggling actress Honey for a side gig, they are hurled into a high-stakes world of action, espionage and betrayal. Years later, as their dangerous past catches up, the estranged Honey and Bunny must reunite and fight to protect their young daughter Nadia.
A Series By Raj & DK

Starring: Varun Dhawan, Samantha, Kay Kay Menon, Simran, Saqib Saleem, Sikandar Kher, Soham Majumdar, Shivankit Parihar, and Kashvi Majmundar. 

Directed by Raj & DK 
Developed by Sita R Menon 
Written by Sita R Menon, Raj & DK 
Produced by D2R Films & Amazon MGM Studios 
Executive produced by The Russo Brothers’ AGBO and Raj & DK 
Executive Producers for All the Series in The World Of Citadel: Anthony Russo, Joe Russo, Angela Russo-Otstot, Scott Nemes, David Weil, Midnight Radio. 
Associate Producer: Anuradha Sharma 
Supervising Producer: Pravin Khairnar (Quercus Productions) 
Director Of Photography: Johan Heurlin Aidt 
Production Designer: Meenal Agarwal 
Editor: Sumeet Kotian 
Screenplay: Sita R Menon, Raj & DK 
Dialogues: Sumit Arora 
Action Directors: Yannick Ben Haddou, Diyan Georigiev Hristov, Aejaz Gulab 
Sound Design: Sanjay Maurya & Allwin Rego 
Background Music: Aman Pant 
Costume Designer: Ameira Punvani 
Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra CSA Second 
Unit Director: Tusshar Seyth 
Associate Director: Chesta Goswami 
Showrunners' Associate: Manisha K Makwana 
First Assistant Director: Moen Sheikh 
Post-Production Supervisor: Jespal Nadar 
Post Production Supervisor: Gautmik 
Post-Production Coordinator: Manisha K Makwana 
Line Producers: Kalyani Warner, Rrahil Deshmukh 
Production Manager: Utkarsha Kohli 
VFX Producer: Variate Studio LLP 
Title Sequence Designed By: Rech Films LLP 
Second Unit Director Of Photography: Tarun Achpal 
Special Advisor: Bimal Parekh

Official Release Date Nov 7, 2024 on Prime Video India.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

Lyrics - 
Re gaam se gori yo muh dhakna padega 
Re laamba laamba ghunghat karna padega
Main padi likhi chhori nyu ghut ghut maru na
Ji laamba laamba ghunghat main to karu na

O samjho madam ji majburi gaam me ghunghat ghana jaruri
Mekeup laari su main mahanga konya Hove ya zid puri
Saasu ladegi tera susra ladega

Is ghunghat aale baane me janu gaadi fasrya thane me
Re london aali feel na leve pagal tu haryane mein
Teri laal pili aankhya te main to daru na

Oh budya ki re chalae marji khule muh te kare allergy
Ghunghat bain karade mera hath jodke kar ree arzi
Ajay hooda ki maan na te raasa chidega

Hindi Lyrics- 
रे गाम से गोरी यो मुंह ढकना  पड़ेगा 
रे लाम्बा लाम्बा  घूंघट करना पड़ेगा 
मैं पढ़ी  लिखी छोरी न्यु घुट घुट मरू ना 
जी लाम्बा लाम्बा घूंघट मैं तो करू ना 

ओ समझो मैडम जी मजबूरी गाम में घूंघट घना जरुरी 
 मेकअप लारी सु मैं महंगा कोन्या होव या  जिद पूरी
 सासु लड़ेगी तेरा सुसरा लड़ेगा 

इस घूंघट आले बाणे में जनू कैदी फसरया  थाने में 
रे लंदन आली फील ना लेव पागल तू हरयाणे में 
तेरी लाल पीली आंख्या ते मैं तो डरु ना 

ओह बुड्या की रे चले मर्जी खुले मुंह ते करे एलर्जी 
घूंघट बैन  करादे मेरा हाथ जोड़के कर री अर्जी 
अजय हुडा की मान ना ते रासा छिड़ेगा

अजय हुडा की मान ना ते रासा छिड़ेगा

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 88 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 15th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: Seedhe Maut - NAMUNA  / SRK
snippet.description:
Written & Performed by Seedhe Maut
Produced by Calm
Mix & Mastered by Hurricane
Animated by Manil

Lyrics
NAMUNA

Hui bando ki thoot choti leli jab lead 
Aadat hai jeet ki roz karu repeat 
Aadat rupees ki I call it cashish 
I told her make a wish poori karu jaise 
Jeez 
Hui bando ki thoot choti fati ni reel 
Bheje mene do emoji kehti its a deal
Hoti rehti bhassad hum bhi chhode koi ni kasar 
Aisi taisi kare magar hume naushu bole chill
Man I got the big guns running 
Chale meri bm khelu jaise most wanted 
Bas SM aur kon hai? Ye pen jaise comet gire panne to pe tu gone hai put the pen in Oppenheimer aise fate jaise bomb hai 
Im a weapon like the seven got em thinking ki ye kon hai gotta tell em kon hai better kon hai launde ke liye problem kon hai con aur kon hai conor kon hai asal me iconic kon hai maut aur Kon hai cheeti 
Kon hai raunak 
kon hai goated 
Kon hai

Vo bole tum hogae ho mainstream 
Hum bole “toh kya, fir bhi best hai”
Rap mera abhi bhi ghar hai
Ye saale yaha abhi bhi guest hai
Jonsi ka banra hai Mantri
Uske Muu pe mukke turant
Khaini chabari hai kamla
Aur kamal ko kamla pasand hai
Ek maali lagara hai gamla
Par andar se khud hai murjhaya
Paisa kama bhi ni paya, aur paisa uga bhi ni paya
Gana zara bhi ni gaaya
To khaana bhi ni khaaya
Premchand ki kahani bhoola par andar ki shiksha bhula hi ni paya
Tere sar pe hai SM ka baadal
Dikhta na soon ae na moon ae
Beta tu pakka namoonahai
Lawde tu pakka namoonahai

Lyrics
SRK

Kari bohot mistakes
Par Chhode nahi dost 
Yaha pe the saanp 
Right under my nose 
Jaladi gaand 
They biting my flows 
Ab bane wo hater 
Im being real right now ab bane wo ghost 
They look at my wrist 
Puche kya hai cost 
Mene kaha mehnat hai bawe ye 
paise se hatke a lot
21 floors 
Jaise final boss 
hai Lagi bahar bheed 
Jaise ander hai shahrukh khan 

Kari mistakes
Par chode ni log
Yaha pe the saanp right under my nose
Ah fuck it mai jaane ni deta hu dushman ko jaise mai jaane ni deta hu dost ko
Pehela mai fuck deta hu apne music ko doosara mai fuck deta hu apne moksh ko 
School se hi aisa hu behen pe baat hai ajati to kho  deta hu apne hosh ko
I mean, mujhe kis baat ki sharm hai
Hu chalte hai karmo pe , ek baat bol tujhe kis baat ka bhram hai 
Jo pal raha hai charno pe
Spit so clean 
Tere dost khade danng hogae
Bando ke beech hum dil ko kaatke bhi baatre ummed
Hum kal se hai behtar aur aaj bhi hai dheet
Na hi jeb se gareeb bas shakal se shareef

Ainth 
Launde rahe mujhse ainth
Leather khole mera bat
Controversies kare catch
Mic pe ni karte hai acting
Inhe hawa lage dikhe ainth

Inki sar hi khole mera bat
Balak rahe humse ainth
Baap ko dikhate ni ainth

Lera hu din ki do flighte
Ye Nashe kyu lage diwaayi se
Iss Office me rehte 2 mic m aur 10 bhai hain yaha Paisa ni laundo yaari kamaayi hai 
Lera hu din ki do flighte
Im working hain velle ye jalte sab bhai se bohot 
Tapke khoon likhu to darte iss Siyahi se 
Ho Jebe wo moti par lagte ho light weight
Hai metal gear solid shit saanpo se bacho 
Wo jaane jab SM ki baari hai bhago 
Ye industry soche ke artist hai thago 
Wo chahte tum sote raho khwaabo me maro bawe fuck that 
Lera hu din ki do flight
Dono bhai hain gucci me jab hota mera showtime 
Inse zyada log hain show pe kyuki likhu more rhymes 
Chahiye ni koi co sign me hu wo jo kare laundo ko sign

Bawe fuck that aage peeche baatein chalein meri 
mera har track hatero ki halak me 10 jaga se phatra hai
Aankho dekhi baato pe bharosa ni, mai suspect
Lapet hi na sake beta it i tu mt fek

Bheja tujhme ni
Bheja mai khuda ka
Beh ja baato me meri 
Yaha bejaan baatein ni banata
Bheji bola kar be lawde tujhe pehele bhi kaha tha
Bheti ganga me jo haath dhoye use pehele dubara hu

Mai kare jau training
Arjun’s aiming
Saare peeche ho jao stay back

Dikhe bas lakshya
Dikhe bas haq hai
Dikhe bas satya hai
Dikhe bas fax
Inhe dikhe bas hate

Dikhe bas fake
Dikhe bas jeb
Dikhe bas cap
Dikhe bas gap
Dikhe bas aib
Dikhe bas lainth
Dikhe bas ainth

snippet.description:
Sri Lanka and West Indies faced each other in the 1st T20I at the Rangiri Dambulla International Stadium. Sri Lanka batted first and posted 179 runs for the loss of 7 wickets. West Indies started the chase well, thanks to Brandon King and Evin Lewis' half-centuries. In the end, West Indies sealed a 5-wicket victory by 19.1 overs.

snippet.title: அமலாவின் புது வீட்டில் எங்களுக்கு மதிய விருந்து/  குழைந்தைகளோடு  போறோம் / VILLAGE  VLOG ,
snippet.description:
அமலாவின் புது வீட்டில் எங்களுக்கு மதிய விருந்து குழைந்தைகளோடு  போறோம் / VILLAGE  VLOG ,

நீங்களும் இது போல கொடுக்க விரும்பினால் முதலில்  எங்களுக்கு  anandhaeswari4@gmail.com என்ற முகவரிக்கு மெயில் செய்யவும் நாங்கள் உங்களை விரைவில் தொடர்பு கொள்வோம்

வணக்கம் நண்பர்களே 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏  
தங்கள் இல்லங்களில் நடைபெறும் அனைத்து விசேஷங்களுக்கும், பிறந்த நாள்,திருமண நாள் திருமண நாள்  நினைவு நாள் மற்றும் இதர விசேஷங்களுக்கும் நீங்கள் எங்கள் மூலமாக சிரமப்படும் மக்களுக்கு உணவு ,உணவு பொருள்கள் ,மற்றும் வீடு இல்லாதவர்களுக்கு வீடு கட்டி கொடுக்க மற்றும் கணவரை இழந்து வருமானம் இன்றி  வாடும் பெண்களுக்கு அவர்களின் வாழ்வாதாரத்திற்கு அவர்களுக்கு ,ஆடு,மாடு, பெட்டிக்கடை,தையல் இயந்திரம் ,மாவு அரைக்கும் இயந்திரம் மற்றும் ஊனமுற்றவர்களுக்கு உதவிகள் ,குழந்தைகளின் படிப்பு செலவுகளுக்கு மற்றும் இன்னும் நிறைய உதவிகள் எங்கள்   My Country Foods சேனல் மூலமாக நீங்கள் செய்ய விரும்பினால்  இந்த மெயில் IDக்கு மெயில் அனுப்பவும்   anandhaeswari4@gmail.com நாங்கள் உங்களை விரைவில் தொடர்பு கொள்வோம்

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 87 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 14th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.description:
#chennairain #chennai #chennairains #rain #chennaites #nammachennai #rainyday 
#tamilnadu​ #Rains​ #weatherupdate​ #tnrains

Awareness video about rain safety

Greater Chennai Corporation (GCC) has issued helpline number 1913 to report rain-related complaints and request rescue operations.

Also Read: Chennai braces for heavy rain, GCC issues essential thunderstorm safety guidelines

snippet.title: Paisa | Official Music Video | @pokhrelkushal858 | @hotstarOfficial Taaza Khabar S2
snippet.description:

IMDb: https://m.imdb.com/name/nm8827769/?ref_=fn_al_nm_1

"Paisa"- A soundtrack from Hotstar Specials' Taaza Khabar Season 2.

Singer- Kushal Pokhrel
Lyricist- Kushal Pokhrel
Composer- Charchill Bhusal

"Paisa" is one of Kushal Pokhrel's (@pokhrelkushal858) hit tracks, exploring how money twists actions and transforms decisions into moves driven by greed. The song perfectly aligns with the gripping storyline of Taaza Khabar Season 2, starring Bhuvan Bam as Vasant Gawde, aka Vasya. This season, Vasya faces off against a vengeful Yusuf Akhtar while battling strained relationships. १ किलो थालीपीठ भाजणी | ३ महिने टिकणारी खमंग थालीपीठाची भाजणी थंडीतला नाश्ता Thalipith Bhajani Recipe

थालीपीठ भाजणी रेसिपी | थंडीसाठी स्पेशल थालीपीठ भाजणी | थालीपीठाची भाजणी रेसिपी | थालीपीठ भाजणी रेसिपी सरिता किचन | खमंग थालीपीठ | थालीपीठ रेसिपी | १ किलो प्रमाणात थालीपीठ भाजणी | ऑर्डर साठी थालीपीठ भाजणी | खुसखुशीत थालीपीठ | थालीपीठ रेसिपी मराठी सरिता |

साहित्य |Ingredients
वजनी प्रमाण (१ किलो थालीपीठ भाजणीसाठी) | Gram Measurements ( For 1kg Thalipith Bhajani Recipe)
 • ज्वारी २०० ग्राम | Jowar 200 gram
 • बाजरी २०० ग्राम | Bajara 200 gram
 • तांदूळ १०० ग्राम | Rice 100 gram
 • गहू १०० ग्राम | Wheat 100 gram
 • हिरवे मूग १०० ग्राम | Green Moong whole 100 gram
 • हरभरा डाळ १०० ग्राम | Chana Daal 100 gram
 • उडीद डाळ ५० ग्राम | Urad Daal 50 gram
 • हरभरे १२५ ग्राम | Whole Chana 125 Gram
 • चवळी ५० ग्राम | Chavali 50 gram
 • जिरे २० ग्राम | Cumin Seeds 20 gram
 • धने २० ग्राम | Coriander Seeds 20 gram
 • मेथीदाणे १ टीस्पून | Fenugreek Seeds 1 tsp

वाटीचे किंवा कप चे प्रमाण |Cup Measurements
 • ज्वारी २ कप | Jowar 2 cups
 • बाजरी २ कप | Bajara 2 cups
 • तांदूळ १ कप | Rice 1 cup
 • गहू १ कप | Wheat 1 cup
 • हिरवे मूग १ कप | Whole Green Moong 1 cup
 • हरभरा डाळ १ कप | Chana Daal 1 cup
 • उडीद डाळ १/२ कप | Urad Daal ½ cup
 • हरभरे १ कप | Whole chana 1 cup
 • चवळी १/२ कप | Chavali ½ cup
 • जिरे १/४ कप | Cumin ¼ cup
 • धने १/२ कप | Coriander seeds ½ cup
 • मेथी दाणा १ टीस्पून | Fenugreek seeds 1 tsp

थालीपीठ भाजणीपासून थालीपीठ रेसिपी |How to make Thalipith using thalipith bhajani
 • थालीपीठ भाजणी ४ वाटी | Thalipith bhajani flour 4 cups
 • मीठ चवीनुसार | Salt to taste
 • बारीक चिरलेली कोथिंबीर दीड वाटी | Chopped Fresh Coriander ⅕ cup
 • बारीक चिरलेला कांदा १ वाटी | Finely chopped onion 1 cup
 • तीळ २ चमचे | Sesame 2 tsp
 • ओवा १/२ चमचा | Carom Seeds ½ tsp
 • हिरवी मिरची ४-५ | Green chilies 4-5
 • लसूण पाकळ्या १०-१२ | Garlic cloves 10-12 
 • जिरे १ टीस्पून | Cumin Seeds 1 tsp
 • हळद १/२ टीस्पून | Turmeric ½ tsp
 • थालीपीठ भाजण्यासाठी तूप / तेल | Ghee or oil to roast thalipith

How to make thalipith bhajani recipe | how to make 1 kilo thalipith bhajani for taking food orders / food business

 • heat up a heavy bottom kadhai & dry roast all the ingredients one by one on very low flame as shown in the video
 • Take all the roasted ingredients onto a clean cotton cloth & allow them to cool down completely
 • Once done, take it to the flour mill & grind. (not grind too fine like all purpose flour, keep it little coarse)

How to make thalipith recipe using bhajani -
 • Grind green chilies, garlic & cumin coarse
 • Into a parat take thalipeeth flour, onion, coriander, sesame, carom seeds, turmeric,  green chilies thecha, salt to taste, mix everything well & knead semi thick dough
 • Take a clean & wet cotton cloth, spread the cloth on a flat surface or on a rolling pin, apply some water
 • Take some dough & make thalipeeth as shown in the video, apply some water to the hands while spreading the thalipith
 • make 4 holes to the thalipith
 • heat up a tawa on med heat, apply some ghee or oil, pur thalipith onto the tawa as shown,
 • cover the thalipeeth for 1 min, and cook on low flame,
 • flip the thalipith, & roast it on medium to high flame, apply some ghee or oil while raosting

 • तीळ २ चमचे | Sesame 2 tsp
 • ओवा १/२ चमचा | Carom Seeds ½ tsp
 • हिरवी मिरची ४-५ | Green chilies 4-5
 • लसूण पाकळ्या १०-१२ | Garlic cloves 10-12 
 • जिरे १ टीस्पून | Cumin Seeds 1 tsp
 • हळद १/२ टीस्पून | Turmeric ½ tsp
 • थालीपीठ भाजण्यासाठी तूप / तेल | Ghee or oil to roast thalipith

How to make thalipith bhajani recipe | how to make 1 kilo thalipith bhajani for taking food orders / food business

 • heat up a heavy bottom kadhai & dry roast all the ingredients one by one on very low flame as shown in the video
 • Take all the roasted ingredients onto a clean cotton cloth & allow them to cool down completely
 • Once done, take it to the flour mill & grind. (not grind too fine like all purpose flour, keep it little coarse)

How to make thalipith recipe using bhajani -
 • Grind green chilies, garlic & cumin coarse
 • Into a parat take thalipeeth flour, onion, coriander, sesame, carom seeds, turmeric,  green chilies thecha, salt to taste, mix everything well & knead semi thick dough
 • Take a clean & wet cotton cloth, spread the cloth on a flat surface or on a rolling pin, apply some water
 • Take some dough & make thalipeeth as shown in the video, apply some water to the hands while spreading the thalipith
 • make 4 holes to the thalipith
 • heat up a tawa on med heat, apply some ghee or oil, pur thalipith onto the tawa as shown,
 • cover the thalipeeth for 1 min, and cook on low flame,
 • flip the thalipith, & roast it on medium to high flame, apply some ghee or oil while raosting

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | RE MANN | Shreya Ghoshal x Swanand Kirkire x Kanishk Seth
snippet.description:
Do you remember what it felt like? The first time you stepped onto campus? Butterflies in your  stomach as you eagerly awaited the world before you. From the joy of personalizing your own nook in the dorm to chatting away with newly made friends in the canteen, these memories will forever remain. 
 
#ReMann will take you on a nostalgic journey through time, while also gently holding the hands of those who are setting out on it for the very first time. Sharing perhaps what they hoped to have known then, India’s most celebrated artists, Shreya Ghoshal and Swanand Kirkire and Kanishk Seth bring to all of us, a warm hug, when it's needed the most. Khayalon se na darr, kal ki chod de fikar!

👁️‍🗨️ Lyrics :

Pari te takraya 
Aaj 1 pari te takraya
Usne dil de aaya 
Main uss ka bhi dil le aaya
Mahra level na kati match kare
Vaa unche mehla aali se
Mane dekhya daur garibi ka
Vaa laada gelya paali se
Uhka husan dekh ke choryo re
Dharti me sir lagge
Dabta na kise sheh te mai
Dhokhe te darr lagey 
Dabta na kise sheh te mai
Dhokhe te darr lagey 

Rang rehgya thoda sanwla
Or rehgya thoda bawla
Tu lage kati hansni 
Bas yhi pe adgya mamla
Re mai desi chora gama ka
Mane duniya ka koy gyaan nahi
Seh lyunga tere dhokhe ne
Mere bhitr itni jaan nahi
Mera chhappr chori kheta mein
Tera city mein ghar lagey
Dabta na kise sheh te mai
Dhokhe te dar lage 
Dabta na kise sheh te mai
Dhokhe te dar lage 

Pyaar karn ka jee mera
Majburi aage adjya hn
Main kalla hu mere yaar nahi
Sab bhari mrpe pdjya hein
Main bhole barga bhola su
Chale dangar dhor te roti re
Rukhi sukhi kha ke raji
Na kehta qismt khotti re
Na kise ke aata khwaaba mein
Na kise ki pau yaadan mein
Yade billa billa hojayegi
Je din fer diye mere baba ne
Main matti hu mane moh nahi
Lohe ke jer lagge
Dabta na kise sheh te mein
Dhokhe te darr lagey
Dabta na kise sheh te mein
Dhokhe te darr lagey

Red alert is issued to Chennai, Kanchipuram, Chengalpattu and Tiruvallur districts of Tamil Nadu after a low pressure is formed in Bay of Bengal. This will continue for the next two days. People living in low lying areas have started parking their cars in safer places and have stated to vacate their houses to live in safe places.

The Greater Chennai Corporation has taken many precautionary steps to avoid urban flooding. They have mobilised relief materials, sucking pumps, have set up helplines, TN Alert app has been released to give updates to the Public.


0:00 - Current state of Chennai?
1:27 - Orange to Red alert 
2:42 - Rain in various parts of Chennai
3:31 - Why is Velachery submerged? 
7:17 - Storm water drainage system 
8:59 - Efforts taken by the government

Red alert is issued to Chennai, Kanchipuram, Chengalpattu and Tiruvallur districts of Tamil Nadu after a low pressure is formed in Bay of Bengal. This will continue for the next two days. People living in low lying areas have started parking their cars in safer places and have stated to vacate their houses to live in safe places.

The Greater Chennai Corporation has taken many precautionary steps to avoid urban flooding. They have mobilised relief materials, sucking pumps, have set up helplines, TN Alert app has been released to give updates to the Public.

Kaffara Episode 86 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 13th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Din Din Diwali - Diwali Anthem | Ft. @YashrajMukhateOfficial, Sarang Sathaye & @Moti-Soap | #BhaDiPa
snippet.description:
#HappyDiwali #Diwali2024 #YashrajMukhate 

BhaDiPa, Moti, Yashraj Mukhate & team Aai aani me are here to make your Diwali more special! Wishes do come true because BhaDiPa is excited to present a brand new fusion music video – Diwali Anthem 2024 to rekindle magical nostalgic memories. Do you remember those childhood Diwali mornings and the joy of a refreshing early dawn bath with scented oil, besan, ubtan and Moti soap? Let’s experience the joy of Diwali pahat, abhyangasnaan and celebrate the festival's dawn in BhaDiPa’s style. If you like this blockbuster Diwali fusion song, share it with everyone! mr.title: दिन दिन दिवाळी - BhaDiPa Diwali Anthem | फि. यशराज मुखाटे, सारंग साठ्ये & @Moti-Soap | #BhaDiPa
mr.description:
भाडिपा, मोती, यशराज मुखाटे आणि टीम आई आणि मी सोबत ही दिवाळी धमाकेदार होणार आहे!!!! दिवाळी पहाट हा मनाच्या जवळचा आणि nostalgic विषय आहे. ह्याच आठवणी ताज्या करण्यासाठी team भाडिपा आई मी आणि यशराज मुखाटे सोबत घेऊन आलंय एक नवीन music video - दिवाळी Anthem 2024!! लहानपणीची दिवाळी पहाट, बेसन, उटणं आणि मोती साबणाने केलेलं अभ्यंगस्नान आठवतं? दिवाळीत सकाळी लवकर उठून पहिली अंघोळ करून दिवाळी पहाट साजरा करण्याची मजा काही वेगळीच होती. चला हीच मजा पुन्हा अनुभवुया भाडिपा style मध्ये! हे blockbuster दिवाळी गाणं तुम्हाला आवडलं असेल तर सगळ्यांसोबत share करा, loop मध्ये चाललं पाहिजे, viral झालं पाहिजे!! भाडिपा, मोती, आई मी आणि यशराज यांच्याकडून तुम्हाला दिवाळीच्या खूप खूप शुभेच्छा!

परंपरा जपण्यासाठी मोतीच कारण मोती साबणाशिवाय दिवाळी आणि अभ्यंगस्नान अपूर्ण आहे! तुमचे मोती साबण आजच घरी घेऊन या. अधिक माहितीसाठी इथे click करा :  https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/blinkit.com/dc/?collection_uuid=15ca5cc5-0f1b-4d7e-8937-c11975018038&utm_source=external&utm_medium=YT&utm_source=Moti__;!!MOA0!aVmcYMHIqTvyX7mBs_14GuV8h48iLlqrXQiUXFLwm6K-IeEEmqEAmPJybICOP8B3ms4w0Mchav1vpyTo6P2uviboL-o_n_Ghp5iEhg$

गायन - यशराज मुखाटे आणि सई गोडबोले
पार्श्वगायन - अल्पना बोंडेकर
संगीतकार - यशराज मुखाटे

रेकॉर्डिंग आणि मिक्सिंग स्टुडिओ - YM स्टुडिओ

यशराज मुखाटे
सारंग साठे
आलोक राजवाडे
मृण्मयी गोडबोले
रेणुका दफ्तरदार
नुपूर शिखरे
अबीर करंडकर
स्वानंद तेंडुलकर
अमेय कदम
मनीषा बोडस
सुहासिनी अनयाल

सहयोगी निर्माता - स्वानंद तेंडुलकर
संकल्पना आणि क्रिएटिव्ह निर्माता - पॉला मॅकग्लिन
दिग्दर्शक - जिजीविशा काळे
डीओपी - निखिल आरोलकर
संपादक - हृषिकेश पेटवे

प्रॉडक्शन डिझाईन - हेनी गुरनासिंघानी
क्रिएटिव्ह डायरेक्टर - सारंग साठ्ये
कार्यकारी निर्मात्या - अश्विनी फाटक
लाइन प्रोड्यूसर - केदार नायडू
कॉस्च्युम डिझायनर - अपूर्वा गुजराती 
एचएमयू डिझायनर - श्रेया दिवेकर
दिशा टीम:
प्रमुख एडी - आकाश शिर्के
इ.स. पहिला - मानसी अनयाल
2रा - तेजस देसाई, कौशल पेडणेकर 
कॅमेरा टीम:
पहिला एसी आणि दुसरा युनिट कॅमेरा - अनिकेत गायकवाड
गॅफर - कुतुब मोंडल
फोकस पुलर - शुभम चौगले 
रोनिन टीम - अमित जैस्वाल, आर्यन जैस्वाल
कॅमेरा असिस्टंट - मंगेश गिरी
असिस्टंट कोरिओग्राफर - देवश्री आठल्ये
बॅकग्राउंड डान्सर्स - पनवेलकर ग्रुप: राहुल निकाळजे, आकाश कांबळे, जय पालकर, नंदिनी गौतम, कांचन पाटील, 
अक्षय शिंदे, चैताली गायकर, प्रवीण जगताप, हृतिकेश नाईक, प्रतीक कोळी, यश मोहिते
मोती मुली - सिया मांडे, काव्यांशी गाडे, वैभवी वर्टीकर
कला संघ:
कला सहाय्यक - पूजा साखरे, संदेश कदम, नदीम खान
आर्टिस्ट पेंटर - नितीन वारे
सेटिंग बॉईज - संतोष दळवी, संजय महामुलकर, रामकृपाल, बासुदेव, उमेश, प्रदीप, रवी, फिरोज रंगसाज, मुन्ना, सोनू, राघवेंद्र गुप्ता, नंदू कुमार, नयन कुमार
विशेष आभार - आदित्य दिवेकर, सूरज ठाकूर, अंकुश कुलाल, आरती भानुशाली कणेकर
पोशाख संघ:
वेशभूषा सहाय्यक - श्रुतिका भांड आणि ईशा दांडेकर 
आउटफिट पार्टनर्स - श्रुती आणि मंगायश, अल्पन्ना क्रिएशन्स, टनक क्लोदिंग, सालंकर कॅप्स, अमोर आउटफिट्स
ड्रेसमन - युग भारसाकळे, राजेश गवई
टेलर - नागेश धांडे
HMU कलाकार - परीक्षित शेटे, जल्पा पटेल, मिसबा शेख
बिझनेस हेड - स्वानंद तेंडुलकर
प्रॉडक्शन मॅनेजर - मंगेश जाधव
लोकेशन व्यवस्थापक - सुरेंद्र मौर्य (कला निर्मिती)
VFX टीम:
VFX स्टुडिओ - इनविमोल्ड पिक्चर्स 
VFX कलाकार - प्रणित गराटे, जयराज वरती, सिद्धेश येंधे, शंतनू कुमटाकर, प्रतीक उमाळे
कलर ग्रेडिंग स्टुडिओ - एआर स्टुडिओ
रंग सुधारणा कलाकार - मुकेश कदम
मीडिया एजन्सी - माइंडशेअर
ब्रँड - मोती
लाईट इक्विपमेंट - स्मार्ट दिवे 
बेस्ट बॉय - रसूल मोनाल
इलेक्ट्रिशियन - मोहम्मद एजाज
कॅमेरा बॉईज - रवींद्र मंडल, सुशांत, सुरेंद्र, मनोज शिंदे, राजन
लाइट बॉईज - अलीम, इमरान, मुन्ना, संतोष, अस्लम, राजा, आलोमगीर, हरीश, हरी राम, राज कपूर, श्री राम, इर्शाद, मन्नान (डीएमएक्स), आलम (डीएमएक्स), जुनैद (ट्रॉली), विष्णू (ट्रॉली) 
रोस्ट्रम बॉईज - संदीप, राजेश, फुलचंद, नारायण

snippet.title: Every Navratri Ever | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
Happy Navratri everyone , May this festive season brings lots of joy into your life like this video . Kaisi lagi video comments me btao 

also Guys to buy Mamaearth Thaali Hair Mask , 
Use Coupon Code : PAAYAL2024
Mamaearth Link: https://bit.ly/3NgORsz

Amazon Link: https://amzn.to/3NfBFUW

Flipkart Link: https://bit.ly/3Nj3Pys

Nykaa Link: https://bit.ly/3Nk4srw

This Video is all about every indian and navratri . what people do on 9 days of navratri . Girls prepping for dandiya nights , buying lehenga choli for the festival season from jwala heri , janpat , gujrati lane , gk market , Sarojini nagar , getting blouse stitched by tailor , buying oxidised jewellery , dressing for the garba with friends and dancing our hearts out and bearing the feet pain after dancing whole night , soaking feet in hot water and salt . Indian aunty looking for girls and lokda for kanjak day . Indian bahu fasting and competing who will do better vrat and saas challenging bahu for do falhari . Sisters fasting on Navratri to loose weight as well as to worship and bribe mata rani to help them pass exams . Indian mom fasting , worshiping durga , cooking tasty vrat ka khana like kuttu ki pakodi , kuttu ke paratha , kuttu ki puri , sabudana khichi , sabudana tikki , samak chawal , samak khichdi , samak pulao , makana kheer , or just doing falahari for the whole middle class family and telling them to fast as well with mom and avoiding pyaaz for 9 days no cooking with onion  . Chintu chinki and savitri preparing for kanjak day  , kids choosing their kajak gifts before hand , mummy cooking bhog chole puri halwa for the kanya . Hoping Kanya will like the navratri gifts . Going out during Navratri shopping bartan , lunch boxes , waterbottle , kanjak gifts for girls and then eating navratri thali . Breaking fast by mistake , overeating during navratri vrat . Bhai behen april fools mom eating onion outside without telling indian mother . Craving gol gappe , indian street food , spicy indian food , chilly potato , samosa , chole bhature , momo , patisse only during the navratri fast and much more
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially mom .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon
Happy Navratri 2024

In "Roob," BOHEMIA delivers his signature lyrical prowess while NOVEEN MORRIS adds a fresh twist, creating a perfect harmony that resonates with fans across the globe. The visuals in this music video are nothing short of stunning, showcasing vibrant scenes that enhance the powerful message of the song.

Don't miss out on this epic musical journey! Remember to like, comment, and subscribe for more incredible content. Hit the bell icon to stay updated on all the latest releases from BOHEMIA and NOVEEN MORRIS!

snippet.title: Sindura Khela Title Song (ସିନ୍ଦୂର ଖେଳ) | Mega Serial | Namita Agrawal | Mon-Sat @ 8 PM | Sidharth TV
snippet.description:
ଖାଲି ନାଁ ନୁହେଁ...ବଦଳିଛି ସମ୍ପର୍କ....
ଏଇ ନୂଆ ସମ୍ପର୍କର ଖେଳ କେଉଁ ନୂଆ ରଙ୍ଗ ନେଇ ଆସିବ ଆଦ୍ୟା ଓ ଅଂଶ ଜୀବନରେ ...?
ଦେଖନ୍ତୁ ସିନ୍ଦୁର ଖେଳ l
ସିଏ ଗଙ୍ଗା ପରି ପବିତ୍ର, ସ୍ନେହ ପ୍ରେମ ମମତାରେ ବାନ୍ଧି ରଖିଥିଲା ନିଜ ପରିବାର କୁ, ହେଲେ ବିଧିର ବିଧାନ ବଡ଼ ବିଚିତ୍ରମୟ, ନିଜ ଭଉଣୀର ଚକ୍ରାନ୍ତ ରେ  ଭାଙ୍ଗି ଗଲା ତା' ସୁଖର ସଂସାର...ନିଜ ସ୍ବାମୀ ଠାରୁ ସିଏ ହେଲା ଅଲଗା l ତା ଦେହରେ ଲାଗିଲା ମିଛ କଳଙ୍କର ଦାଗ, ଦୁଇଟି ପିଲାଙ୍କୁ ଜନ୍ମ ଦେଲା ସତ, ହେଲେ ଗୋଟେ ପିଲା ହଜିଗଲା କେଉଁ ଏକ ଦୁର୍ଘଟଣା ରେ l ଏ ହେଉଛି ଆମ ଆଦ୍ୟାର ଜୀବନ କାହାଣୀ,
ଅଂଶବି ହେଇଚି ଷଡ଼ଯନ୍ତ୍ରର ଶିକାର, ଆଦ୍ୟା କୁ ହରେଇ ସିଏ ଏବେ ଏକା, କେଉଁ ଏକ ଅଜଣା ସନ୍ତାନ କୁ ଆଶ୍ରୟ ଦେଇଛି ସିଏ, ଜାଣେ ନାହିଁ କିଏ ତା'ର ମା...? କଣ ତା'ର ବଂଶ ପରିଚୟ ?
ଏ ପିଲା ଦୁହିଁଙ୍କ ଭିତରେ କଣ ଅଛି ସମ୍ପର୍କ ..? ପିଲା ଦୁଇଟି କଣ କେବେ ଏକାଠି ହେଇ ପାରିବେ...? ଆଦ୍ୟା ଅଂଶଙ୍କର ପୁଣି ଥରେ ଯୋଡ଼ି ପାରିବକି ଭାଙ୍ଗି ଯାଇଥିବା ସମ୍ପର୍କ...?
ଏ ସବୁର ଉତ୍ତର ପାଇବାକୁ ଗଲେ ଦେଖୁଥାନ୍ତୁ ସିନ୍ଦୁର ଖେଳ

ଅଂଶବି ହେଇଚି ଷଡ଼ଯନ୍ତ୍ରର ଶିକାର, ଆଦ୍ୟା କୁ ହରେଇ ସିଏ ଏବେ ଏକା, କେଉଁ ଏକ ଅଜଣା ସନ୍ତାନ କୁ ଆଶ୍ରୟ ଦେଇଛି ସିଏ, ଜାଣେ ନାହିଁ କିଏ ତା'ର ମା...? କଣ ତା'ର ବଂଶ ପରିଚୟ ?
ଏ ପିଲା ଦୁହିଁଙ୍କ ଭିତରେ କଣ ଅଛି ସମ୍ପର୍କ ..? ପିଲା ଦୁଇଟି କଣ କେବେ ଏକାଠି ହେଇ ପାରିବେ...? ଆଦ୍ୟା ଅଂଶଙ୍କର ପୁଣି ଥରେ ଯୋଡ଼ି ପାରିବକି ଭାଙ୍ଗି ଯାଇଥିବା ସମ୍ପର୍କ...?
ଏ ସବୁର ଉତ୍ତର ପାଇବାକୁ ଗଲେ ଦେଖୁଥାନ୍ତୁ ସିନ୍ଦୁର ଖେଳ

snippet.title: Iyer को कैसे लगी Bhide के घर पे चोट? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Renovation
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Jethalal is stopped by Bhide and Abdul as they recognized that Jethalal is wearing two different shoes. Meanwhile, Babita calls Iyer and inquires about the availability of Plumber. What will be Jetha’s reaction when he finds the truth about his shoes? Why Babita is worried? To know, watch the full episode.


Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2024 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah

snippet.title: #Video | Chumma Chumma | चुम्मा चुम्मा | Khesari Lal Yadav | Shilpi Raj | Rajaram | नया भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
देखि Chumma Anthem Of The Year अउरी तैयार हो जाई रवुआ सब झूमे खातिर ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और आकांशा पूरी के साथ "चुम्मा चुम्मा " पे।'

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Title :- Chumma Chumma
Singer :- Khesari Lal Yadav & Shilpi Raj
Feat :- Akanksha Puri
Film Name:- Rajaram
Film Director:- Parag Patil
Song Director :- Sooraj Katoch (Zenith)
Lyrics :- Pinku Baba
Music :- Vinay Vinayak 
Choreographer :- Geeta Tamta (Zenith)
Dop- Rahul Yadav 
Editor :- Anand Kumar (Santu)
Associate Dop - Priyanshu Vats 
Focus Puller- Chandan Singh
Dance troupe :- Zenith
Dance Group :- (PK) Kamlesh 
GFX :- Suraj Vishwakarma 
DI :- Rohit Singh 
Production :- Amit Singh
All Costume:- Reema (Zai fashion )
Makeup Hair:- Vikash Kumar and Aryan Rajesh

Film Credits:

Production:- Technician Film Factory 
Producers :- Parag Patil & R.R. Prince

Lyrics:-

F-  फ्लेक्सी कमरिया पे नजरें गड़ाते हो 
     क्या बात है जो ये डॉलर उड़ाते हो 
M- लाली देखाके ललचावत बाड़ू 
      सुतल फीलिंग के जगावत बाड़ू 
      त दे द ना एगो नमूना 
      चूमा चूमा दे द, चूमा चूमा दे द चूमा 
F- चूमा चूमा ना देम, चूमा चूमा ना देम चूमा 

                     अंतरा -1
F-  अरे इंस्टा की मै तो रानी हूँ 
      तेरे जैसे हैँ फैन लाखों में 
      क्यूँ दूँ मै तुझे चुम्मा 
      सपना देखो बस रातों में 
M- द मौका, ल मौका -2
      गारंटी बा मजा आई हो 
      नाही देबू त दुख होइ दूना 
      चूमा चूमा दे.........

     
                   अंतरा -2
F-  मेरा चुम्मा तो बड़ी महँगा है
     बोलो क्या दोगे मुझे चुम्मे का 
     अरे मेकप में बड़े खर्चे हैँ 
     रेट लाखों हैँ मुझे छूने का 
M-  द खरचा, के परचा -2
      सब डॉलर में दे दियाई हो 
      बा रइसी रानी बुझ तु उ ना 
      चूमा चूमा दे...
